@startuml sequence_uc1

title UC-1 — Valutazione clinica completa

skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #534AB7
    ActorBorderColor #534AB7
    LifeLineBorderColor #888780
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F1EFE8
    ParticipantBorderColor #534AB7
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #EEEDFE
    ParticipantFontColor #3C3489
    BoxBorderColor #B4B2A9
    BoxBackgroundColor #F1EFE8
}

actor "Medico" as Client

box "Infrastruttura" #F1EFE8
    participant "API Gateway\n:9000" as GW
end box

box "Prosumer" #EEEDFE
    participant "Care Coordinator\n:9203" as CC
    participant "Clinical Aggregator\n:9202" as CLA
    participant "Diagnostic Aggregator\n:9201" as DA
end box

box "Provider" #E1F5EE
    participant "Anagrafe\n:9101 (SOAP)" as AN
    participant "Farmacia\n:9103" as FA
    participant "Laboratorio\n:9102" as LAB
    participant "Imaging\n:9104" as IMG
end box

== Request ==

Client -> GW : GET /api/coordinator/patients/{patientId}/fitness-assessment
GW     -> CC : GET /patients/{patientId}/fitness-assessment

== Parallel execution ==

par Branch 1 — clinical profile
    CC  ->> CLA : GET /patients/{patientId}/profile
    CLA ->  AN  : getPatientById · getMedicalHistory · getAllergies\n[SOAP]
    AN  --> CLA : PatientData + MedicalHistory + Allergies
    CLA ->  FA  : GET /patients/{patientId}/prescriptions
    FA  --> CLA : List<Prescription>
    CLA --> CC  : ClinicalProfile

else Branch 2 — diagnostic bundle
    CC  ->> DA  : GET /patients/{patientId}/diagnostics
    DA  ->  LAB : GET /tests/orders?patientId={id}&status=COMPLETED
    LAB --> DA  : List<TestResult>
    DA  ->  IMG : GET /patients/{patientId}/reports
    IMG --> DA  : List<ImagingReport>
    DA  --> CC  : DiagnosticBundle
end

== Synchronization barrier ==

note over CC : CompletableFuture.allOf(diag, clin).join()

== Risk analysis & response ==

CC  --> GW     : FitnessReport · List<RiskFlag>
GW  --> Client : 200 OK · FitnessReport

@enduml
